---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const effectiveDate = 'March 20, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Center for Psychological Treatment and Assessment"
  description="Privacy Policy for the Center for Psychological Treatment and Assessment website, including information about contact forms, Google Analytics, and website privacy practices."
>
  <Navbar />

  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-40 md:pb-24 bg-[#fcfbf9] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-[20%] left-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[60%] bg-[#e0eae5] rounded-full opacity-60 blur-3xl lg:blur-[80px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[-10%] w-[35%] h-[50%] bg-[#fdf3df] rounded-full opacity-60 blur-3xl lg:blur-[80px]"></div>
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-10 text-center relative z-10">
      <p class="text-[15px] xl:text-lg font-bold text-[#2f594f] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Privacy</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl xl:text-[72px] font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] leading-tight tracking-tight mb-8">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected, used, and protected when you visit this website or contact the practice online.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-500 font-medium">
        Effective date: {effectiveDate}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 xl:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-10">
      <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700">
        <div class="bg-[#fcfbf9] border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            When you use this website, we may collect information you choose to provide, such as your name, email address, and the contents of a message you submit through a contact form. We may also collect limited technical information automatically through analytics tools, such as device type, browser type, pages visited, and general location information based on IP address.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#fcfbf9] border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">How We Use Information</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Information collected through this website may be used to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <li>respond to inquiries and requests for consultation,</li>
            <li>communicate about services offered by the practice,</li>
            <li>improve website performance, content, and user experience, and</li>
            <li>maintain the security and functionality of the website.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#fcfbf9] border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Contact Forms and Communications</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you submit a form on this website, your message is processed through website service providers and delivered to the practice by email. Please do not submit urgent, emergency, or highly sensitive medical information through website forms.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Website forms are intended for general inquiries, scheduling requests, and initial contact only. If you are experiencing an emergency, call 911 or go to the nearest emergency room.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#fcfbf9] border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Analytics and Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            This website uses Google Analytics 4 to understand website traffic and general visitor behavior. Google Analytics may use cookies or similar technologies to collect information such as page visits, browser details, and approximate location information.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            This website does not currently use advertising or remarketing tools for targeted advertising. You can manage cookies through your browser settings if you prefer to limit tracking technologies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#fcfbf9] border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">How Information Is Shared</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Information may be shared with service providers that help operate this website and process submitted messages, such as website hosting, form handling, analytics, and email delivery providers.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            We do not currently sell personal information through this website. Information may also be disclosed if required by law or to protect the rights, safety, or security of the practice, website users, or others.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#fcfbf9] border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational measures are used to help protect information submitted through the website. However, no website or internet transmission can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#fcfbf9] border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Children&apos;s Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            This website is not intended to collect personal information directly from children without appropriate parental or guardian involvement. If you believe information has been submitted in error, please contact the practice so it can be reviewed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#fcfbf9] border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Your Choices and Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Depending on where you live, you may have privacy rights under applicable law, including rights to request access to, correction of, or deletion of certain personal information.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            To make a privacy-related request or ask a question about this policy, please contact the practice using the information below.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#fcfbf9] border border-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            This website may link to third-party websites, resources, or services. Those third parties operate under their own terms and privacy practices, and this Privacy Policy does not apply to them.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#d1f3f1] border border-[#b8d6c9] rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p><strong>Center for Psychological Treatment and Assessment</strong></p>
            <p>1320 Tower Rd, Suite 156, Schaumburg, IL 60173</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@centerforpta.com" class="text-[#2f594f] font-semibold hover:underline">info@centerforpta.com</a></p>
            <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+18472300045" class="text-[#2f594f] font-semibold hover:underline">(847) 230-0045</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          This page provides general website privacy information and is not legal advice. If you need legal guidance for your practice, please consult a qualified attorney familiar with U.S. privacy laws and healthcare-related requirements.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
